<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٦٤٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5178">قَبِيصَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ </a>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/941">بِشْرُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3875">عَبْدُ اللهِ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2638">الْأَعْمَشِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2809">أَبِي وَائِلٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6088">مَسْرُوقٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«مَا رَأَيْتُ أَحَدًا أَشَدَّ عَلَيْهِ الْوَجَعُ مِنْ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>